      "alt": "A paperback book titled \"Lectures on Phase Transitions and the Renormalization Group\" by Nigel Goldenfeld rests on a dark, textured carpet. The book has a white cover with a dark blue band at the top reading \"FRONTIERS IN PHYSICS\" and a small horizontal strip near the middle featuring four abstract physics diagrams. The author's name is printed within a dark blue rectangle near the bottom, right above the initials \"ABP\".",
